body_html:
Currently, the constants for HE are prohibitive. I don't see this changing. I know less about MPC.

I'm not sure this FR is useful, since it is so broad. I will close it for that reason. I think if someone wanted to make a specific proposal of how to support either in TF, that would be quite welcome.
